# PJR Website — project skills

This repo vendors full skill packs under `.agents/`. **Before** writing marketing copy, optimizing conversions, planning SEO, or designing UI, read the relevant `SKILL.md` from the appropriate pack.

## Marketing ([coreyhaines31/marketingskills](https://github.com/coreyhaines31/marketingskills))

- **Location:** `.agents/marketingskills/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md`
- **Start here:** `.agents/marketingskills/skills/product-marketing-context/SKILL.md` — align work with `.agents/product-marketing-context.md` in this repo.
- **Common tasks:** `copywriting`, `page-cro`, `form-cro`, `seo-audit`, `schema-markup`, `site-architecture`, `analytics-tracking`, `ai-seo`, `social-content`, etc.

## UI / UX ([nextlevelbuilder/ui-ux-pro-max-skill](https://github.com/nextlevelbuilder/ui-ux-pro-max-skill))

- **Primary:** `.agents/ui-ux-pro-max-skill/.claude/skills/ui-ux-pro-max/SKILL.md`
- **Related:** `design-system`, `design`, `ui-styling`, `brand`, `banner-design`, `slides` under `.agents/ui-ux-pro-max-skill/.claude/skills/`

## Project stack

- Vite, vanilla HTML/JS, Tailwind CSS (`tailwind.config.js`, `src/style.css`).
- Prefer accessible, healthcare-appropriate patterns (trust, clarity, WCAG-minded contrast) per UI skill checklists.

## Updating skills

To refresh vendored repos:

```bash
cd .agents/marketingskills && git pull
cd ../ui-ux-pro-max-skill && git pull
```
